snippet.title: Nicktoons Racing -  GBC Longplay/Walkthrough #112 [4Kp60]
snippet.description:
Rating: 1.5/5

Positives: Nice selection of characters, Has a bit of charm

Negatives: AI is wacky, Always bouncing off walls, Controls, Just not fun imo, Sometimes if you don't get the right item RNG you can;t actually beat the race before the time is up which results in a game over
